  "title": "Construction Supervisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong></p><p>HDC PROJECT PTE. LTD.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will apply your renovation knowledge and technical skills to support project tasks, working efficiently within a team environment over a six-day workweek.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Drive company vehicles safely and responsibly using a valid Class 3 driving license to support project logistics</li><li>Apply renovation knowledge to assist in technical tasks and contribute to project completion</li><li>Learn and adapt quickly to new processes and techniques to improve work quality and efficiency</li><li>Collaborate with team members to complete daily tasks within scheduled work hours</li></ul><p><strong>Required competencies and certifications</strong></p><ul><li>Valid Class 3 driving license</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Strong technical skills related to renovation work</li><li>Ability to learn new skills quickly</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information</strong></p><ul><li>Work schedule: 6 days per week</li></ul>",
